# ⏳ Thread Methods

## sleep()

Pauses the current thread.

```java id="2t4k7j"
try {

    Thread.sleep(2000);

} catch(Exception e) {

}
```

---

## join()

Waits for another thread to finish.

```java id="tfrc8g"
t1.start();

t1.join();

System.out.println("Main Thread");
```

---

## isAlive()

Checks whether a thread is running.

```java id="qv2kv4"
System.out.println(t1.isAlive());
```

---

## getName()

Returns thread name.

```java id="93qov9"
System.out.println(Thread.currentThread().getName());
```

---

## setName()

Changes thread name.

```java id="ldk6ea"
t1.setName("Worker Thread");
```

